Run this after downloading and extracting proftpd archive:
./configure --help --> check options
./configure --prefix=/opt/proftpd
make	--> will do multiple compilations of the source files
sudo make install	--> will make necessary directories

go to /opt/proftpd
then go to sbin/
run sudo  ./proftpd &	--> to run in the background

ps -ef | grep proftpd
or
pgrep -l proftpd

pkill proftpd	--> to stop it

./proftpd -n	--> run in the foreground


/opt/proftpd/etc/proftpd.conf	--> where the server configuration file is

To access the server: ftp://localhost


